reagent-name-parasite-infection-fluid = parasite infection fluid
reagent-desc-parasite-infection-fluid = A viscous biological fluid containing parasitic organisms.

reagent-name-antiparasitic = antiparasitic drug
reagent-desc-antiparasitic = A powerful medicine that kills parasites and reduces infection levels. Extremely toxic to parasitic organisms.

reagent-name-parasite-growth-accelerator = parasite growth accelerator
reagent-desc-parasite-growth-accelerator = An experimental drug that accelerates parasite growth in exchange for host tissue regeneration. May cause parasitic limb growth.
